msgctxt "Talk13"
msgid ""
"<1.so>New to the art of Goron massage,\n"
"I take it? That's OK. First time for\n"
"everything, as they say.\n"
"<2.so>A Goron-style massage is done on top of\n"
"a hard rock bed. <3.pa>Pressure is applied to\n"
"your body to squeeeeze the tension out.\n"
"<4.so>But I'll tell ya, it doesn't hurt one bit.<5.pa>\n"
"Mostly.<6.pa> Honestly, I doze off sometimes!\n"
"\n"
"When it's all over, you'll sleep like a\n"
"rock and feel great when ya wake up.<7.pa>\n"
"You'll be all limber and full of energy!"
msgstr ""

