"<2.se_co>Rudania <3.re_co>has stopped stirrin' up trouble,<4.pa>\n"
"and the <5.se_co>magma bombs <6.re_co>have stopped too!\n"
"\n"
"Of course, I don't go outside,\n"
"so it makes no difference to me.\n"
"\n"
"<7.so>Anyhoo... <8.pa>Time to get back to business!"
